			<description><![CDATA[<p>
Technical Support Engineers provide knowledgeable front-line technical support service to our customers in a prompt, cheerful, and professional manner. Technical Support Engineers operate using our 24/7/365 support helpdesk and/or live chat system. Ideal candidates must possess extraordinary customer service skills and understand that going &quot;above and beyond&quot; is our normal way of doing business.</p>
<p>
Minimum requirements for this position are:</p>
<ul>
<li>
At least 18 years of age or older</li>
<li>
Excellent written English. Candidates with poor English comprehension cannot be considered.</li>
<li>
Reliable high-speed Internet connection</li>
<li>
Minimum of 3 years experience in customer service in a position that requires daily customer interaction</li>
<li>
Minimum of 1 year experience working with Linux-based servers with cPanel control panel</li>
<li>
Must be familiar (but not necessarily an expert) with all of the following: cPanel, WHM, Apache, LiteSpeed, CloudLinux, PHP, MySQL, Unix shell, email (POP/IMAP/SMTP), FTP, DNS, and many other common service protocols used in the web hosting industry</li>
<li>
Ability to work under pressure, and multi-task in a fast-paced environment</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>We will consider applications from remote candidates, however, outsourcing or employment agencies need not apply. We will only consider applications from <u>individuals</u> not companies or multiple persons.</strong></p>
<p>
This is a <strong>remote, work-from-home</strong> opportunity, however, all prospective candidates must understand that we expect that shift schedules be strictly adhered to, and that during your shift we expect that Eleven2 work will be all that you work on. We expressly forbid having outside hosting industry employment, even outside your Eleven2 shift.</p>
<p>
We are currently hiring for <strong>all shifts</strong>. Please indicate your shift preference/availability in your application below.</p>
<p>
<strong>NO PHONE CALLS OR EMAILS ABOUT THIS POSITION! PLEASE APPLY USING THE FORM BELOW! WE WILL CONTACT CANDIDATES THAT WE ARE INTERESTED IN, THERE IS NO NEED TO FOLLOW-UP.</strong></p>
